window.bookSummaryJSON = "Katie MacAlister, best-selling author of paranormal romantic comedies, ignites a devilishly lusty story with <i>Light My Fire</i>. The gorgeous Aisling Grey, introduced in <i>You Slay Me</i>, juggles being a demon lord, a Guardian, and a wyvern's mate all at once - though not always successfully. Recently relocated to London, Aisling and her doggie demon sidekick, Jim, are eager for a fresh start. Drake the hunky dragon, however, has other plans for her."; 
